# Format: pid  arrival_ms  burst_ms  nice  io_ratio  policy  rt_prio  deadline_ms  name
#
# policy:   CFS(0) FIFO(1) RR(2) BATCH(3) IDLE(5) NN
# nice:     -20..19  (CFS/BATCH only, ignored for RT)
# rt_prio:  1..99    (FIFO/RR only)
# io_ratio: 0.0..1.0 (fraction of time doing I/O — triggers random sleep events)
# deadline: 0 = no deadline; N = must finish within N ms of arrival
#
# pid  arr   burst  nice  io     policy  rtp  dl    name
1      0     80     0     0.30   CFS     0    0     bash
